-- intro

mod10
  $ segment 64
  $ pF "vibrato" (range 1 1.5 $ fast 0.5 saw)
  # pF "vrate" (range 2 5 $ fast 0.3 rand)
  # tremolorate (range 5 7 $ slow 11 $ sine)
